{"id":12497,"date":"2021-08-31T16:13:19","date_gmt":"2021-08-31T09:13:19","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=12497"},"modified":"2021-08-31T16:13:19","modified_gmt":"2021-08-31T09:13:19","slug":"lien-doanh-hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-nen-tang-thuong-mai-dien-tu","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/lien-doanh-hyundai-thanh-cong-trien-khai-nen-tang-thuong-mai-dien-tu\/","title":{"rendered":"LI\u00caN DOANH HYUNDAI TH\u00c0NH C\u00d4NG TRI\u1ec2N KHAI N\u1ec0N T\u1ea2NG TH\u01af\u01a0NG M\u1ea0I \u0110I\u1ec6N T\u1eec"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u00ean doanh\u00a0<\/em><em>\u00d4<\/em><em>\u00a0t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eadn<\/em><em>\u00a0h\u00e0nh<\/em><em>\u00a0n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed giai<\/em><em>\u00a0\u0111o\u1ea1n 1<\/em><em>, nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u00ean phong v\u1ec1 mua s\u1eafm tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn trong ng\u00e0nh \u00f4 t\u00f4.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a HTV trong vi\u1ec7c n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u Hyundai n\u00f3i ri\u00eang v\u00e0 v\u1edbi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 t\u00f4 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00f3i chung. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cl\u00ean s\u00e0n\u201d ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1eabu SUV 7 ch\u1ed7 Hyundai Santa Fe th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 mua s\u1eafm m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/shop.hyundai.tcmotor.vn\/\">https:\/\/shop.hyundai.tcmotor.vn\/\u00a0<\/a><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-12499\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1873\" height=\"864\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90.jpg 1873w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90-300x138.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90-1024x472.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90-768x354.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90-1536x709.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90-240x111.jpg 240w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/211b27ef2281d6df8f90-540x249.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1873px) 100vw, 1873px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1ch m\u1ea1ng c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 (4.0) v\u1edbi tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n kinh t\u1ebf s\u1ed1, th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n hay t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0o n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u00f9ng l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb t\u1ee5t h\u1eadu v\u1edbi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HTV c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed mang l\u1ea1i, c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng ri\u00eang d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u tham kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn mua c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng xe c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng. HTV x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m mua xe v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14\/06\/2021, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n mua xe Hyundai Santa Fe c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a h\u00e3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, showroom tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/shop.hyundai.tcmotor.vn\/\">https:\/\/shop.hyundai.tcmotor.vn\/<\/a>\u00a0tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y 6 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu Santa Fe th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi\u00a0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, showroom tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin: gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 trang b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng xe, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd hi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 xe m\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, d\u00f9 \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u b\u1ea5t k\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd n\u00e0o c\u00f3 xe li\u00ean h\u1ec7 t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c li\u00ean quan.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-12498 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1855\" height=\"841\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d.jpg 1855w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d-300x136.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d-1024x464.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d-768x348.jpg 768w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d-1536x696.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d-240x109.jpg 240w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/8bb31d72191ced42b40d-540x245.jpg 540w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1855px) 100vw, 1855px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u201cH\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1nh tay n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m mua s\u1eafm ti\u1ec7n \u00edch v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n Covid-19 \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1eddi cam k\u1ebft l\u1ea5y kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0m tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean doanh Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng. Th\u1eddi gian ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eabu xe h\u01a1n l\u00ean tr\u00ean h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh chi\u1ebfc Santa Fe v\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng y\u00eau th\u00edch\u201d. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a HTV chia s\u1ebb.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Li\u00ean doanh\u00a0\u00d4\u00a0t\u00f4 Hyundai Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam (HTV) ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u1eadn\u00a0h\u00e0nh\u00a0n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed giai\u00a0\u0111o\u1ea1n 1, nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trong k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u00ean phong v\u1ec1 mua s\u1eafm tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn trong ng\u00e0nh \u00f4 t\u00f4. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1